ENTRY            40703   20251006   20260319   20260319       4226
SUBENT        40703001   20251006   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                 10         37
TITLE       The investigation of the reaction Na-22(n,p)Ne-22
            for a neutron energy to 1,000 eV
AUTHOR     (Yu.M.Gledenov,J.Kvitek,S.Marinova,Yu.P.Popov,J.Rigol,
           V.I.Salatski)
REFERENCE  (J,ZP/A,308,57,1982)
           (C,82ANTWER,,150,1982)
           (S,INDC(CCP)-235,(2),388,1984)=(C,83KIEV,2,388,1983))
            In Russian
           (R,JINR-P3-82-303,1982)
INSTITUTE  (4ZZZDUB)
REL-REF    (O,41400002,Yu.M.Gledenov+,R,JINR-P3-89-351,1989)
            Final data for Cl-35 ( Table 1 of
            S,INDC(CCP)-235,(2),388,1984) WID
           (O,41352003,Yu.M.Gledenov+,J,PAN,62,818,1999)
            Final data for Cl-35  Table 1 of
            S,INDC(CCP)-235,(2),388,1984)  WID/STR
           (O,41596002,Yu.M.Gledenov+,J,ZP/A,322,685,1985)
            Final data for Cl-36 ( the same as in
            S,INDC(CCP)-235,(2),388,1984 Table 1)
FACILITY   (REAC,4ZZZDUB) IBR-30 pulsed reactor.
METHOD     (TOF) TOF base from 20 m to 85 m.
            Li-6 was used for energy calibration and normalization
           of cross-sections.
DETECTOR   (SIBAR,IOCH)
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Type of uncertainty is not explained in the
            article.
HISTORY    (19840410C) Compiled at the CJD
           (19870506U) One reference added -report JINR-P3-82-303
           (20010319A) Date is corrected
           (20231113A) EN-MAX=1000.eV was deleted from COMMON
            block of Subent 001.
            Upper -> lower case correction.
            BIB information was updated.
            Reaction was corrected in Subent 002.
            Subent 003 was added.
           (20251006A) Ref. S,INDC(CCP)-235 was added.
            Subents 004, 005 were added.
ENDBIB              37
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           40
SUBENT        40703002   20251006   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                  8         30
REACTION  1(11-NA-22(N,0),,EN)
          2(11-NA-22(N,EL),,WID/RED)
          3(11-NA-22(N,P),PAR,WID)
SAMPLE      Na-22 sample on polycarbon layer of 500 microCurie on
            a polycarbon film of 4 micrometer thickness.
            Li-6 or B-10 was placed on inverse side.
METHOD     (TOF)
           Run number  Resolution,microsec  Measuring time,hr
            1            4.5                  48.
            2            0.2                  91.
            3            3.0                  47.
DETECTOR   (SOLST) Silicon semiconductor detector of 8 cm2 area,
           202 micrometer thick sensitive layer, placed at 40 mm
           from samples. Registered protons up to ~ 5.2 MeV.
ANALYSIS    Breit-Wigner formula was used to calculate resonance
            parameters at fitting of measured cross-section.
STATUS     (TABLE,,Yu.M.Gledenov+,J,ZP/A,308,57,1982)
            Text on page 59.
            Text page 150 of 82ANTWER,,150,1982
            Text page 389 of S,INDC(CCP)-235,(2),388,1983
           (DEP,40703002) Cross-section measured.
COMMENT    Of compiler. DATA 3 (GAMMAp1) in :
           abstract of ZP/A,308,57,1982,
           82ANTWER,,150,1982,
           text page 389 of INDC(CCP)-235,(2),388,1984
           - 114+-20 eV.
HISTORY    (20231113A) PAR was added in Reaction 3.
            MOMENTUM L2 and E 3 were added.
           (20251006) DATA 3 were corrected :
            45.+-20. -> 114.+-20. eV - see comment of compiler.
ENDBIB              30
