DATA      3DATA-ERR  3
EV         EV         NO-DIM     EV         EV         MEV
EV         EV
  145.       11.       0.         1.6        0.2        2.25
 114.       20.
ENDDATA              6
ENDSUBENT           41
SUBENT        40703003   20251006   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                  9         26
REACTION   (11-NA-22(N,P)10-NE-22,,SIG)
SAMPLE      Na-22 sample on polycarbon layer of 500 microCurie on
            a polycarbon film of 4 micrometer thickness.
            Li-6 or B-10 was placed on inverse side.
MONITOR    (3-LI-6(N,T)2-HE-4,,SIG)
           (5-B-10(N,A)3-LI-7,,SIG)
            Li-6 and B-10 were used for determination of the
           energy dependence and absolute value of neutron flux
           and for the energy calibration of spectrometer.
           ((MONIT)11-NA-22(N,P)10-NE-22,,SIG) At thermal energy.
MONIT-REF  (,S.F.Mughabghab+,R,BNL-325,1973) 3rd edition.
            Li cross section.
           ((MONIT)30586002,J.Kvitek+,J,ZP/A,299,187,1981)
            at thermal energy.
DETECTOR   (SOLST) Silicon semiconductor detector of 8 cm2 area,
           202 micrometer thick sensitive layer, placed at 40 mm
           from samples. Registered protons up to ~ 5.2 MeV.
METHOD     (TOF)
           Run number  Resolution,microsec  Measuring time,hr
            1            4.5                  48.
            2            0.2                  91.
            3            3.0                  47.
ERR-ANALYS . Quantization errors:
            scale X - 0.324 %, scale Y - 0.328 %.
STATUS     (CURVE,,Yu.M.Gledenov+,J,ZP/A,308,57,1982) Fig.3
HISTORY    (20231113C) Subent was added.
ENDBIB              26
